<HL>
   Higher Profits
   Are Expected
   For Toy Makers
   ---
   Dearth of Big Draws Causes
   More-Even Distribution
   Of Sales Among Firms
   ----
   By Joseph Pereira
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
12/26/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
<CO>
   FPP GAL HAS J.NTD J.SEL MAT TOY TTI
</CO>
